data.description: What is it that you need in a home in South Georgia? A community pool, a clubhouse, a climate-controlled fitness facility, and a fire pit area! This property has all these exciting community amenities close by and also great outdoor activity possibilities around pond areas in charming Richmond Hill. This well-kept home includes 4 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, and a spacious loft! An office/flex room is located just off of the extended foyer spotlighting glass double doors. Luxury vinyl plank flooring leads through the first floor with an open concept for the dining room, kitchen, and living room area. All bedrooms are located on the second floor and 3 bedrooms are equipped with walk-in closets for lots of storage. This beautiful home also features a spacious loft on the second floor that creates endless possibilities! The attic has added floorboards for extra storage, the garage has epoxy flooring and hanging storage racks that make this home just not like the others! Schedule your showing today!!! SELLERS ARE OFFERING TO HAVE HOME FRESHLY PAINTED OR ASSIST WITH CLOSING COSTS!
